{"TopicId":143024,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Building a Reusable Spaceplane [STOCK]","CreatedByName":"JYNg","CreatedById":165975,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T13:55:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JYNg","CreatedById":165975,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T13:55:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPreviously I\u0027ve tried to launch a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E but to no avail: you just can\u0027t seem to do that with low-tier tech. So I\u0027ve decided to approach the problem with a different solution: a spaceplane on top of a reusable first stage. The design will be similar in concept to Dyna-Soar and Boeing X37-B.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/4VWeQ/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-03T20:02:13Z\u0022 title=\u002207/03/2016 08:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by JYNg\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdditional information\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Van Disaster","CreatedById":58876,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T14:36:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou *can* \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E at really low tiers, it\u0027s just not a good idea. Glad to see you got your aerodynamics sorted in the end.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour method scales well, provided you keep your aero balance with the boost stage:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://flic.kr/p/GRo1XC\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://c3.staticflickr.com/8/7176/26813074714_498f83137a_b.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u002226813074714_498f83137a_b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://flic.kr/p/HMaDva\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002227421751975_8259f0ee22_b.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://c8.staticflickr.com/8/7565/27421751975_8259f0ee22_b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://flic.kr/p/HmYiW1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002227147944000_3d73e2d62d_b.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://c1.staticflickr.com/8/7461/27147944000_3d73e2d62d_b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://flic.kr/p/HJnaTS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002227390050956_064748363c_b.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://c5.staticflickr.com/8/7122/27390050956_064748363c_b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-03T14:41:20Z\u0022 title=\u002207/03/2016 02:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Van Disaster\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}